# ============================================
# EAS Build ignore — used INSTEAD of .gitignore when present (Expo 공식 동작).
# ============================================
# 목적: git 에는 절대 커밋하지 않는(.gitignore 유지) Firebase CLIENT config
#   (google-services.json/.dev.json + GoogleService-Info.plist/.dev.plist)를
#   `eas build --local`/클라우드 아카이브에는 **포함**시켜 프로덕션 로컬 빌드가 찾도록 한다.
#   서버 시크릿(서비스계정 키, OAuth 시크릿)은 빌드에도 절대 포함하지 않는다.
# [주의] 이 파일이 있으면 EAS 는 .gitignore 를 무시하므로, 아래는 .gitignore 전체를
#   복제하고 credentials 섹션만 조정한 것이다. .gitignore 를 바꾸면 여기도 동기화할 것.
# ============================================

# ===========================================
# Go Build Artifacts
# ===========================================
bin/
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
cover.out
cover.html
cpu.prof
mem.prof

# ===========================================
# Build Artifacts & Distribution
# ===========================================
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
*.egg

# Mobile build artifacts (Android/iOS binaries — may embed google-services / signing config)
*.apk
*.aab
*.ipa

# ===========================================
# Python Cache & Bytecode
# ===========================================
__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.rdb
*.dbm

# ===========================================
# Virtual Environments
# ===========================================
venv/
.venv/
env/
.env/
.uv_cache/
.uv-cache/

# ===========================================
# Test Coverage
# ===========================================
.coverage
coverage.json
htmlcov/

# ===========================================
# IDE & Editors
# ===========================================
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*.sw?
*~
.cursor/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.suo
.#*

# ===========================================
# OS Files
# ===========================================
# Mac
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
.DocumentRevisions-V100
.fseventsd
.Spotlight-V100
.TemporaryItems
.Trashes
.VolumeIcon.icns

# Windows
[Dd]esktop.ini
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db

# Linux
.directory

# ===========================================
# Logs & Temporary Files
# ===========================================
*.log
logs/
*.tmp
*.temp
*.bak
*.backup

# ===========================================
# Backups
# ===========================================
.moai-backups/
*.backup/
*-backup/
*_backup_*/

# ===========================================
# Secrets and Credentials (CRITICAL)
# ===========================================
# Environment files
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.production.example

# Certificate files
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
*.jks

# Private keys (specific patterns to avoid false positives)
*-key.*
*_key.*
*.key.*
*-secret-key.*
*-api-key.*
api-key-*
secret-key-*
private-key*
*-secret.*
*_secret.*
*.secret.*
secret-*.*

# Credential patterns in environment files
*_secret=*
*_token=*

# Cloud provider credentials
.aws/config
.aws/credentials

# ===========================================
# Project credentials
# ===========================================
# repo-root credentials/ (서비스계정 키·OAuth 시크릿 포함) — 빌드 아카이브에서 전부 제외.
/credentials/

# apps/mobile/credentials/ — Firebase CLIENT config(google-services.json/.dev.json +
#   GoogleService-Info.plist/.dev.plist)는 로컬 프로덕션 빌드가 필요로 하므로 **포함**한다
#   (.gitignore 의 `credentials` 패턴이 git 커밋은 계속 막는다 — 여긴 EAS 빌드 전용).
#   단, 서버 시크릿은 빌드에도 절대 넣지 않는다:
apps/mobile/credentials/*service-account*.json
apps/mobile/credentials/*oauth*.json
apps/mobile/credentials/moyura-web-oauth.json
apps/mobile/credentials/.DS_Store

# ===========================================
# Claude Code Configuration
# ===========================================
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/settings.local.*.json
.claude/.env.local*
.claude/local/
.claude/plans/
.claude/agent-memory/
.claude/worktrees/

# Skill-specific credentials
.claude/skills/*/.env*
.claude/skills/*/secrets/
.claude/skills/*/*/*secret*
.claude/skills/*/*/*key*
.claude/skills/*/*/*token*
!.claude/skills/*/modules/*token*.md

# ===========================================
# Local-Only Files (never sync via git pull)
# ===========================================
.moai/status_line.sh
.moai/memory/
.moai/worktrees/
.moai/cache/

# ===========================================
# Evolution Telemetry (local-only usage data)
# ===========================================
.moai/evolution/telemetry/*.jsonl
!.moai/evolution/telemetry/.gitkeep

# ===========================================
# Node.js (for docs/Nextra)
# ===========================================
node_modules/
*.tsbuildinfo
.tscache/
.next/
out/

# ===========================================
# Build Tools & Frameworks
# ===========================================
.turbo/
.nuxt/
dist-ssr/

# ===========================================
# Deployment & CI/CD
# ===========================================
.vercel/
.netlify/
.firebase/

# ===========================================
# Monorepo Tooling (pnpm + Nx)
# ===========================================
.nx/cache
.nx/workspace-data
.pnpm-store/
.pnpm-debug.log*

# Expo / React Native (root-level safety net)
.expo/

# Native build artifacts (iOS CocoaPods)
**/ios/Pods/
